channel.title: Spacesuit Floating Away From The ISS
channel.description:
[url='https://videosift.com/video/Eerie-footage-of-a-spacesuit-floating-away-from-the-ISS']https://videosift.com/video/Eerie-footage-of-a-spacesuit-floating-away-from-the-ISS[/url]
Unbeknownst to the general public, the spacesuit actually contains the body of an ISS astronaut, that nobody can stand. We're really witnessing the perfect murder.
This will be the premise for Gravity 2, starring Sandra Clooney and George Bullock, coming soon to a theater near you.
